{"tid":566423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【揭秘侵侵訪華】美官員帶核彈手提篋入見習總 國安阻攔爆「大戰」","createTime":"2018-02-20T02:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T02:59:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9329f07ca8600800b590a7c7e83f9dac47a093d3","tid":566423,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519057727_905c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519057727_905c.jpg&h=1e24e970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，美國傳媒揭發，美總統特朗普去年11月出訪中國時，因受權發動核攻擊的手提箱「核足球」（nuclear football），而引發了一場「中美大戰」。<br />\n<br />\n美媒《Axios》報道，特朗普當日出訪北京，進入人民大會堂與中國國家主席習近平會面。其間中國國家安全局人員一度阻止攜帶「核足球」的美國軍官入內。<br />\n<br />\n一位美國官員趕忙向白宮幕僚長凱利（John Kelly）報告。凱利聽到後趕過去，走到提箱官員前讓他繼續前行，並告訴該名軍事助理及周圍美國官員「我們進去」（we are moving in），隨即有中國安保人員抓住凱利的胳膊，凱利隨即甩開對方的手。<br />\n<br />\n之後美國特勤人員上前抓住了該名安保人員，並將其按倒在地。Axios強調，雙方肢體衝突發生在一瞬間，中方人員絕對沒有碰到手提箱，之後北京安保方面的負責人向美方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180220/57851947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57851947&d=K1RdEzaG75tE%2F7zQtc754aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ce84bdba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57851947&h=ebf51860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180220/57851947</a>"},{"pid":"261c25e64766b88fa8b694ab04341a1d9a9f9e59","tid":566423,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"支那點解要道歉"},{"pid":"d9a6df5eaa474da3e22dde7d02b95bf58ad8c6ba","tid":566423,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f6834d1320e85abe233c9cef3b09e45a73a29f","tid":566423,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"笑4😂"},{"pid":"eda898c1a4925dbe3961b3b74b934488ce1628a3","tid":566423,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"侵侵識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a522b2f2844f96c3c89e21482374d2e135a101b","tid":566423,"uid":33875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"又唔係帶個核彈入去"},{"pid":"a0c0b1565fd83aa5537f946762e3d2300b92e27d","tid":566423,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a522b2f2844f96c3c89e21482374d2e135a101b","tid":566423,"uid":33875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"又唔係帶個核彈入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"習大大驚死人暗殺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac601647317e6540dca66cffc30dfc4f1c5da205","tid":566423,"uid":1696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4a522b2f2844f96c3c89e21482374d2e135a101b","tid":566423,"uid":33875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"又唔係帶個核彈入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"的確唔係帶一支核彈<br />\n佢帶緊幾千支核武器入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d083a1e60cacaf30be9d3c79cfb588b5c60b94","tid":566423,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0952daa2237d3197250f1cce6501a3f91ac7737","tid":566423,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01d083a1e60cacaf30be9d3c79cfb588b5c60b94","tid":566423,"uid":5770